{"tid":711410,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【買樓非必賺】新地兩個樓盤   揸七年都要輸","createTime":"2018-06-21T13:37:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-24T12:21:18.000Z","uid":68476,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d5a50e7cfce63f4b3ecda70ce6da698f0c5bde0a","tid":711410,"uid":68476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T13:37:01.000Z","msg":"【買樓非必賺】新地兩個樓盤   揸七年都要輸<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180621/large/1529578859_0b61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180621%2Flarge%2F1529578859_0b61.jpg&h=61ca0ee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n星堤蝕讓主要集中當年賣逾千萬的貴價單位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180621/large/1529578860_0131.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180621%2Flarge%2F1529578860_0131.jpg&h=828a59d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n筲箕灣譽‧東<br />\n<br />\n新地(016)樓向來受歡迎，但兩個於2011年開售的新樓，卻連環錄蝕讓。<br />\n<br />\n土地註冊處資料顯示，屯門星堤再錄「流血」成交，位於3座一個複式B室特色單位，實用面積1,874方呎，剛以1,920萬元連1個車位沽出，呎價10,245元平過同區龍珠島。原業主為許碧，與北京合康變頻董事長劉錦成的妻子同名，不排除為同一人，該單位於2011年5月向新地以2,035萬元買入，再於2013年斥70萬元購入該車位，現連車位一併出售，賬面已貶值185萬元，若計及釐印費及佣金等開支，連使費<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">料蝕逾280萬元</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n屯門孤島龍珠島別墅上月錄得一宗破頂成交，呎價高近1.2萬元。<br />\n<br />\n除了星堤，同屬新地樓的筲箕灣譽‧東亦再錄蝕讓。涉及一個高層B室單位，實用面積670方呎，成交價1,230萬元，呎價18,358元。原業主2011年向新地以1,204.4萬元買入，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">樓價7年升幅僅2.1%，扣使費後，明賺實蝕</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef717c24ccfd6ad718b34b03788028e49ee3abc3","tid":711410,"uid":135957,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-21T14:57:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e514fe8dae14a6b9e2b9893163e6d04e21cd50df","tid":711410,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:10:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6eafb4e39260516aedf7d651f33850564f51cd2b","tid":711410,"uid":172861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-22T06:23:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef90576cca58f8ea24358f6ea98665b691abbe8b","tid":711410,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f4bb84ab661c52a934953562f6cf9ea5f550452","tid":711410,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:58:00.000Z","msg":"星堤位置好差"},{"pid":"d23b6ea97a77c457eb5ccf870d74f1d832e76b02","tid":711410,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef90576cca58f8ea24358f6ea98665b691abbe8b","tid":711410,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T02:59:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T03:58:33.000Z","msg":"御半山呢d極品位置唔知會點"},{"pid":"3c68c7411e2ecf707827d0bec18559b2c2c5b8d7","tid":711410,"uid":10509,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T04:00:17.000Z","msg":"星堤行返出去最近巴士站都要最少15 分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e862bf5f8d0f69d399c00c66d9155b8b5e51a12","tid":711410,"uid":135957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T12:21:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}